    "DRUG -ABUSE:Associated with meeting the criterion of evidence of drug abuse, current or past, you might encounter terms such as substance abuse, addiction, positive drug screen, toxicology report, withdrawal symptoms, tolerance, dependency, rehabilitation, relapse, narcotics, stimulants, depressants, hallucinogens, drug -seeking behavior, overdose, and history of substance use disorder.",
